12
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:40,980
=Are You The One=

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episode 40=

14
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,280
To impeach

15
00:01:45,790 --> 00:01:47,840
Cui Xingzhou, Lord Huaiyang,

16
00:01:51,150 --> 00:01:53,350
for abusing the favor
of royal family to be greedy,

17
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:55,590
keeping Traitor Lu's property for himself,

18
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,070
not handing illegal assets
over to the National Treasury,

19
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:00,120
embezzling military funds,

20
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,590
seizing estates on his own,

21
00:02:01,950 --> 00:02:03,040
bribing officials heavily,

22
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:05,680
acting without shame,

23
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,950
and disrupting the court's order.

24
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,910
Lord Huaiyang

25
00:02:10,310 --> 00:02:11,630
concealed private assets?

26
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,120
Yes.

27
00:02:13,470 --> 00:02:15,590
Cui Xingzhou took advantage of his position

28
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:18,310
to keep money that should
belong to the National Treasury.

29
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:21,270
Traitor Lu's property

30
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,590
has been fully reported.

31
00:02:24,490 --> 00:02:26,030
The Ministry of Revenue and the Ministry of War

32
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,080
both verified it.

33
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,280
What else could be hidden?

34
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,080
This, this, this...

35
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:35,710
Ten days ago,

36
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:39,190
The Minister of Revenue inspected
the land deeds in the capital

37
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:41,190
and found that many deeds

38
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:43,310
had been tampered with and transferred.

39
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,240
Upon investigation,

40
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,080
the Ministry of Revenue's Secretary

41
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,280
Wen Tinghe confessed.

42
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,470
It was illegal property

43
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,000
of Traitor Lu,

44
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,150
which was hidden under the cover

45
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:54,960
of his wealth as the Prince.

46
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,750
We then followed the clues.

47
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,310
Cui Xingzhou

48
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:02,710
did contribute to the suppression
of Traitor Lu.

49
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,640
However,

50
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:05,190
in Dongzhou and the capital,

51
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,560
a lot of the traitor's properties

52
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,710
were misappropriated

53
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,430
to become his private wealth.

54
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:12,750
Duke.

55
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:17,470
Why are you framing me?

56
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,470
Cui Xingzhou.

57
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:21,910
Do you think

58
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,750
that with Wen Tinghe dead,

59
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,310
there would be no evidence?

60
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,430
(The Register)
The bureaus and I

61
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:41,190
secretly investigated Traitor Lu's
hidden assets for days

62
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,240
and tracked down accomplices.

63
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,750
You embezzled money and violated the law.

64
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,710
We found the witness and irrefutable evidence.

65
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:50,120
Cui Xingzhou,

66
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:54,750
though our families have a marriage alliance,

67
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,870
I cannot turn a blind eye

68
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:59,000
to your unforgivable crimes.

69
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,280
I'm innocent.

70
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,870
I truly feel unfortunate for my family

71
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,430
to be associated with the Guo family,

72
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:10,400
a treacherous family
that frames loyal ministers,

73
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:13,310
and have a marriage alliance with you.

74
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:19,920
The Regent condoned

75
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:22,190
his adopted daughter to poison His Majesty.

76
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:24,120
This crime has not yet been charged.

77
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,510
You are already forming factions
and attacking dissenters

78
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:29,430
and even regarding him as the leader
of the ministers.

79
00:04:32,430 --> 00:04:33,390
Fine.

80
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:38,000
I would like to see

81
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,510
who is truly the traitor to the nation.

82
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,160
Let's wait for His Majesty to wake up.

83
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,190
He will make a clear judgment.

84
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:53,870
Fellow officials, did you see that?

85
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,190
Cui Xingzhou is

86
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:58,950
so arrogant due to his achievements

87
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,310
that now he

88
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:02,160
looks down on everything.

89
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:07,040
Now that His Majesty is critically ill,

90
00:05:07,830 --> 00:05:09,040
how can we allow a traitor

91
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,070
who deceives the public and perverts the law

92
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,750
to act arrogantly in the court?

93
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:17,510
He should be apprehended now and sent

94
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,870
to the Court of Judicial Review.

95
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,240
He should be interrogated there

96
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,950
for us to find out his crimes
and uphold the national law.

97
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:28,240
We agree.

98
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,270
We should apprehend him

99
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:32,270
to uphold the national law.

100
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,110
Chief Judge Zhang,

101
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,050
I am here.

102
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,610
You're in charge of the Court
of Judicial Review.

103
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,070
You shall be fair and just.

104
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:05,190
Now, Lord Huaiyang

105
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,240
is handed over to you.

106
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,880
I shall

107
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:09,830
go to the inner palace

108
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,430
to report this petition

109
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:13,920
and ask Grand Empress Dowager

110
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,680
about her decree.

111
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:18,120
Regent, we follow your command.

112
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,440
Guards,

113
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,950
arrest Cui Xingzhou!

114
00:06:24,270 --> 00:06:25,110
Yes.

115
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,630
Lord Huaiyang embezzled
the traitor's property in Dongzhou,

116
00:07:15,190 --> 00:07:17,040
and is involved in several major cases.

117
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,290
He's detained in the Court of Judicial Review,

118
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,750
awaiting further orders.

119
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:22,720
No one from the Cui family shall

120
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:24,680
leave the capital without permission.

121
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:25,960
This special notice

122
00:07:26,310 --> 00:07:28,120
will be executed by the responsible parties.

123
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:41,480
- Open the door.
- Yes.

124
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,240
Lord Huaiyang,

125
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,510
back then, you and Liu Yu

126
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,190
pretended to fight over a woman.

127
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:12,630
He treated you like nothing

128
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,040
and you treated him as an enemy.

129
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,950
I was almost deceived

130
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,240
by you two.

131
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,240
And now,

132
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,190
your plans have failed.

133
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:28,480
One has become a poisoned wreck,

134
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,390
and the other a prisoner who embezzled money.

135
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:33,840
You made one wrong move,

136
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,960
and lost the entire game.

137
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,510
Lord Huaiyang, don't worry.

138
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,910
I won't kill you

139
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,080
immediately.

140
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:46,600
I must witness how you, a man so proud,

141
00:08:47,630 --> 00:08:49,320
watch your enemy

142
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:51,240
climb to the pinnacle

143
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:53,320
of the Imperial Court step by step,

144
00:08:53,550 --> 00:08:55,480
and destroy the most important things to you

145
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:59,200
in a flip of the hand.

146
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,390
For example,

147
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:06,480
that delicate Princess-

148
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,440
What did you do to her?

149
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,720
I'm asking you. What have you done?

150
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,790
Calm down.

151
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:20,150
Liu Miantang is now

152
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,030
a criminal's wife.

153
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,910
Naturally, she's confined in the mansion,

154
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,000
awaiting further orders.

155
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:27,320
During these days,

156
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,670
she can live peacefully,

157
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:34,480
or get slapped every day.

158
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,550
You can beg me.

159
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:39,750
I can have Liu Miantang

160
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,790
transferred here

161
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:42,240
to be locked up with you.

162
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,030
How about a reunion with your wife?

163
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,200
Cui Xingzhou,

164
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:04,320
I'm giving you one last chance.

165
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,440
Kneel before me.

166
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,440
And I guarantee she can live.

167
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:15,910
The Lord commands you to kneel.

168
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:16,800
Stand down!

169
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,320
Kneel.

170
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:31,750
Kneel in front of me!

171
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,080
My Lord.

172
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,040
- My Lord.
- You, you.

173
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:50,350
My Lord.

174
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,480
Crazy! You are crazy!

175
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,670
Yes, I'm crazy.

176
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,870
Even if I fall into the hell,

177
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:58,320
I will crawl up from it!

178
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:02,480
For anyone who failed to kill me,

179
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,270
I will make them pay back

180
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,240
a thousandfold!

181
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:08,630
How about that?

182
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:11,790
Do you want to kill me now, or wait until you

183
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,150
ascend the throne to grant me a death

184
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,390
by a thousand cuts
or by tearing me apart by chariots?

185
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,040
Your Lordship,

186
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,080
you better ascend the throne quickly.

187
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:24,510
Otherwise, when His Majesty wakes up,

188
00:11:24,550 --> 00:11:25,390
you

189
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:27,600
will be the real traitor.

190
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,360
The one kneeling and begging

191
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,790
for mercy from me in this prison

192
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,720
will be you, Liu Pei!

193
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,550
I will kill you now!

194
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:38,800
My Lord.

195
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,200
Fine.

196
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,240
As you wish.

197
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:49,120
Tonight, I will ascend the throne.

198
00:11:49,630 --> 00:11:51,670
By then, you must listen to the death knell

199
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,150
at the city gate carefully.

200
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,320
Close the door.

201
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:05,900
(Abdication Edict)

202
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:21,750
Mother, where is your

203
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:26,000
Imperial Seal?

204
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,720
I have forgotten.

205
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:37,590
It doesn't matter.

206
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,320
I have plenty of time

207
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,480
to wait for you to remember.

208
00:12:44,790 --> 00:12:45,630
But...

209
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:49,440
But Liu Yu does not have time.

210
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,630
Liu Pei, Prince Sui,

211
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:56,390
is of noble character,

212
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,390
and deeply resembles the Late Emperor.

213
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,360
He is surely capable of inheriting the throne.

214
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:05,920
Son,

215
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,670
on this Edict,

216
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:12,440
which line is true about you?

217
00:13:12,510 --> 00:13:14,320
Mother, even if you don't acknowledge it,

218
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,240
Liu Yu has no heir,

219
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,320
and I am the only one,

220
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:22,120
who can inherit the throne.

221
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:25,720
As long as His Majesty is still alive,

222
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:30,000
I will never condone you.

223
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,080
Mother, are you really insisting on this?

224
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:40,200
The Imperial Court of Qi Kingdom is leaderless.

225
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,630
Lords of various states

226
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:43,000
will all act upon hearing the news,

227
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,150
like wolves and tigers eyeing the prey.

228
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:49,080
As long as you give me the Imperial Seal,

229
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:51,960
and make this Edict legitimate,

230
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,870
the chaos will cease.

231
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:56,670
Mother, you will only become

232
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,000
more noble than you are now.

233
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,320
Mother,

234
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:06,360
I really don't understand

235
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,510
why every time,

236
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:11,030
you always side with others.

237
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:15,550
We are blood relatives.

238
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:17,630
Why can't the throne

239
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:19,440
be given to me?

240
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,510
Pei.

241
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:23,910
- Mother.
- You.

242
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,480
Grand Empress Dowager, Prince Sui,

243
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,600
The Imperial Medical Institute

244
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,710
said that His Majesty's condition

245
00:14:28,710 --> 00:14:29,550
has suddenly improved.

246
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:30,720
Several physicians found

247
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,910
a way to detoxify.

248
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,080
- Move aside.
- Pei.

249
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:37,120
Where are you going?

250
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,240
Mother, please

251
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,600
remember as soon as possible

252
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,510
where the Imperial Seal is.

253
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:55,390
Pei.

254
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,550
Stop! Who are you?

255
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:05,510
Officer,

256
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:07,510
I'm from Duke Qing's Mansion.

257
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:09,200
By the order of Her Ladyship,

258
00:15:09,270 --> 00:15:10,750
I'm delivering food to Lord Huaiyang.

259
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:14,500
(Inspection of Prison)

260
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,100
(Permission for meal delivery.
Do not obstruct.)

261
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:22,750
Open the door.

262
00:15:55,270 --> 00:15:56,840
Your Lordship, eat while it's hot.

263
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,040
After tonight, maybe

264
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,510
you can never eat.

265
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,040
You-

266
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:20,870
I'm here

267
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:23,750
by the order of Grand Empress Dowager,

268
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,750
to care for His Majesty.

269
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,910
Everyone, leave.

270
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,440
My Lord.

271
00:16:29,510 --> 00:16:30,510
His Majesty can be saved.

272
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:31,590
The poison can be

273
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:32,750
neutralized in a few days.

274
00:16:32,870 --> 00:16:34,510
Everyone, leave!

275
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:35,680
- Yes.
- Yes.

276
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,790
Prince Sui is not keeping his promise

277
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:58,720
of letting me live

278
00:16:58,720 --> 00:16:59,670
till he takes the throne.

279
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,480
But he also said,

280
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,440
if a criminal tries to escape,

281
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,160
he'll be killed without mercy.

282
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:07,240
Why are you laughing?

283
00:17:07,470 --> 00:17:08,310
The last time I heard

284
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:09,680
the words 'killed without mercy',

285
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,280
they were from you.

