00:42:09,150 --> 00:42:14,620
♪No one knows love's outline like I do♪

580
00:42:15,640 --> 00:42:21,230
♪Under the dew, dreams rest,
the hairpin returns to the moon♪

581
00:42:22,110 --> 00:42:26,680
♪Holding your hand, we gather many blossoms♪

582
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:28,110
Honey, you suffer from seasickness.

583
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:29,840
Why did you take the water route?

584
00:42:30,150 --> 00:42:32,190
Taking the land route would
cost us too much time.

585
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:33,120
I can't wait any longer.

586
00:42:33,510 --> 00:42:34,350
Can't wait for what?

587
00:42:37,550 --> 00:42:38,710
Is it for you all to see?

588
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:39,640
Put it down.

589
00:42:41,070 --> 00:42:41,910
Put it down.

590
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:45,440
I can't wait to return to Zhenzhou

591
00:42:45,590 --> 00:42:46,710
to be a lord

592
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:48,920
who are spoiled.

593
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:50,320
By then, dear,

594
00:42:50,590 --> 00:42:52,630
you must manage our livelihood well,

595
00:42:53,190 --> 00:42:55,440
so that you can support your husband.

596
00:42:57,280 --> 00:42:58,840
Since you want to rely on me,

597
00:42:59,030 --> 00:43:00,630
you must reserve your strength.

598
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:01,840
Otherwise,

599
00:43:02,070 --> 00:43:03,070
I'm not supporting you.

600
00:43:04,630 --> 00:43:06,190
Right now, all I have left

601
00:43:06,190 --> 00:43:07,110
is my strength.

602
00:43:08,440 --> 00:43:09,360
For the next few days,

603
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:11,440
we need to carefully plan

604
00:43:11,590 --> 00:43:12,840
our future.

605
00:43:14,000 --> 00:43:15,480
Finally, we are going home.

606
00:43:17,280 --> 00:43:18,230
Our home.

607
00:43:19,650 --> 00:43:25,660
♪When the day comes that the sky and river
merge into one color♪

608
00:43:26,080 --> 00:43:31,970
♪The light boat passes by,
and the wind carries a love song♪

609
00:43:34,190 --> 00:43:36,480
My spoiled husband gets seasick again.

610
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:38,670
Let's see if you can muster the strength now.

611
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:42,000
Wait, let me try again.

612
00:43:42,780 --> 00:43:47,010
♪Having a good sleep by your side
with the moon as a pillow♪

613
00:43:47,030 --> 00:43:47,870
Oh, no,

614
00:43:48,070 --> 00:43:48,910
I still feel dizzy.

615
00:43:52,470 --> 00:43:58,920
♪If we arrive at crossroads♪

616
00:43:59,370 --> 00:44:05,020
♪There must be someone on their way home♪

617
00:44:06,450 --> 00:44:11,130
♪On their way home♪

618
00:44:17,540 --> 00:44:20,380
(The End)

619
00:44:36,221 --> 00:44:42,451
♪The boat drifts,
bringing back the sunset♪

620
00:44:43,451 --> 00:44:49,571
♪When we reunite, we still joke
about the cause and effect♪

621
00:44:50,561 --> 00:44:56,811
♪Who passed by, the crabapple
falls with a turn♪

622
00:44:57,941 --> 00:45:01,181
♪Loving rightly but choosing wrong♪

623
00:45:01,521 --> 00:45:06,101
♪With joys, sorrows, partings and reunions♪

624
00:45:06,701 --> 00:45:13,361
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

625
00:45:14,111 --> 00:45:17,481
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

626
00:45:17,771 --> 00:45:21,101
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

627
00:45:21,281 --> 00:45:28,051
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

628
00:45:28,431 --> 00:45:35,201
♪Long hidden in the eyes,
flickering in and out♪

629
00:45:35,701 --> 00:45:42,111
♪Let go of the flowers blooming
in the yard last night♪

630
00:45:42,951 --> 00:45:49,361
♪Let go of the waves in the stream
in half a lifetime♪

631
00:45:49,941 --> 00:45:56,561
♪Let those dust and chaos go on endlessly♪

632
00:45:57,361 --> 00:46:00,781
♪In this lifetime, my wish is to the vast sky♪

633
00:46:00,781 --> 00:46:05,881
♪There are many more♪

634
00:46:06,261 --> 00:46:12,981
♪Everyone travels far, seeing clouds and snow♪

635
00:46:13,551 --> 00:46:17,181
♪Always hard to stay, yet easy to part♪

636
00:46:17,181 --> 00:46:20,581
♪Crossing spring waters and autumn trials♪

637
00:46:20,581 --> 00:46:27,491
♪A couple under the moonlight,
can stay together♪

638
00:46:27,781 --> 00:46:34,631
♪Time flows as we dream through four seasons♪

639
00:46:35,001 --> 00:46:38,581
♪I wish to journey with you forever♪

640
00:46:38,581 --> 00:46:41,691
♪Year after year♪

641
00:46:43,421 --> 00:46:47,721
♪For many years to come♪
